2-2-2-2-2--2/"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://fantabulosity.com/nutella-cheesecake-no-bake-filling-baked-brownie-crust/#faq-question-1674361469973","position":1,"url":"https://fantabulosity.com/nutella-cheesecake-no-bake-filling-baked-brownie-crust/#faq-question-1674361469973","name":"Should you bake the crust of a no-bake cheesecake?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Nope! That's the beauty of this no-bake recipe; even the crust doesn't have to be baked.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://fantabulosity.com/nutella-cheesecake-no-bake-filling-baked-brownie-crust/#faq-question-1674361404761","position":2,"url":"https://fantabulosity.com/nutella-cheesecake-no-bake-filling-baked-brownie-crust/#faq-question-1674361404761","name":"Why is my No-Bake Cheesecake gooey?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It's possible that the cheesecake may not have chilled enough. Place it in the freezer to allow it to \"set\" and see if that helps.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://fantabulosity.com/nutella-cheesecake-no-bake-filling-baked-brownie-crust/#faq-question-1674362030562","position":3,"url":"https://fantabulosity.com/nutella-cheesecake-no-bake-filling-baked-brownie-crust/#faq-question-1674362030562","name":"How do you store no-bake Nutella cheesecake?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"You can store this cheesecake in the refrigerator for 4-5 days.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://fantabulosity.com/nutella-cheesecake-no-bake-filling-baked-brownie-crust/#faq-question-1665318594364","position":4,"url":"https://fantabulosity.com/nutella-cheesecake-no-bake-filling-baked-brownie-crust/#faq-question-1665318594364","name":"Can you freeze Nutella cheesecake?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes! You can freeze this cheesecake for up to 3 months. After 3 months it can start to develop freezer burn. ","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Recipe","name":"Oreo Nutella Cheesecake","author":{"@id":"https://fantabulosity.com/#/schema/person/bf935f632ead60ef98ee98161d9242f8"},"description":"Oreo Nutella Cheesecake - This homemade, smooth, Nutella cheesecake filling that&#039;s on top of a buttery Oreo crust, is an easy dessert that you can make ahead of time!","datePublished":"2023-01-21T18:00:00+00:00","image":["https://fantabulosity.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Oreo-Nutella-Cheesecake-22-copy.jpg","https://fantabulosity.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Oreo-Nutella-Cheesecake-22-copy-500x500.jpg","https://fantabulosity.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Oreo-Nutella-Cheesecake-22-copy-500x375.jpg","https://fantabulosity.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Oreo-Nutella-Cheesecake-22-copy-480x270.jpg"],"recipeYield":["8","8 servings"],"prepTime":"PT15M","totalTime":"PT315M","recipeIngredient":["2 cups crushed Oreos","¼ cup salted butter (melted)","16 ounces cream cheese (2 - 8 oz. boxes)","¾ cup granulated sugar","½ cup heavy whipping cream","1 teaspoon vanilla extract","½ cup Nutella"],"recipeInstructions":[{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Use a fork to stir together the crushed Oreos and the melted butter in a medium sized bowl. Once the ingredients form a wet, sandy mixture, press the mixture into a standard 9-inch springform pan.","name":"Use a fork to stir together the crushed Oreos and the melted butter in a medium sized bowl. Once the ingredients form a wet, sandy mixture, press the mixture into a standard 9-inch springform pan.","url":"https://fantabulosity.com/nutella-cheesecake-no-bake-filling-baked-brownie-crust/#wprm-recipe-23537-step-0-0"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"In a separate medium sized bowl, use an electric hand mixer to whip the cream cheese until it is smooth and creamy.","name":"In a separate medium sized bowl, use an electric hand mixer to whip the cream cheese until it is smooth and creamy.","url":"https://fantabulosity.com/nutella-cheesecake-no-bake-filling-baked-brownie-crust/#wprm-recipe-23537-step-0-1"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Add the granulated sugar, heavy cream, and vanilla extract. Use the electric hand mixer to incorporate the added ingredients to the cream cheese until the mixture is homogenous.","name":"Add the granulated sugar, heavy cream, and vanilla extract. Use the electric hand mixer to incorporate the added ingredients to the cream cheese until the mixture is homogenous.","url":"https://fantabulosity.com/nutella-cheesecake-no-bake-filling-baked-brownie-crust/#wprm-recipe-23537-step-0-2"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Whisk in the Nutella until no clumps of Nutella remain in the cream cheese mixture.","name":"Whisk in the Nutella until no clumps of Nutella remain in the cream cheese mixture.","url":"https://fantabulosity.com/nutella-cheesecake-no-bake-filling-baked-brownie-crust/#wprm-recipe-23537-step-0-3"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Pour the cream cheese mixture into the springform pan and cover with plastic wrap. Allow the cheesecake to sit in the freezer for at least 5 hours. (Some freezers may require longer, and it may even be safe to freeze it for 24 hours, to guarantee it will set.","name":"Pour the cream cheese mixture into the springform pan and cover with plastic wrap. Allow the cheesecake to sit in the freezer for at least 5 hours. (Some freezers may require longer, and it may even be safe to freeze it for 24 hours, to guarantee it will set.","url":"https://fantabulosity.com/nutella-cheesecake-no-bake-filling-baked-brownie-crust/#wprm-recipe-23537-step-0-4"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Slice and enjoy!","name":"Slice and enjoy!","url":"https://fantabulosity.com/nutella-cheesecake-no-bake-filling-baked-brownie-crust/#wprm-recipe-23537-step-0-5"}],"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":"5","ratingCount":"4","reviewCount":"4"},"review":[{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"reviewBody":"YUM!!! I love this delicious version!!!","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Erin | Dinners,Dishes and Dessert"},"datePublished":"2018-09-01"},{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"reviewBody":"So yummy! A chocolate lover's dream :)","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jamielyn"},"datePublished":"2018-09-01"},{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"reviewBody":"YUM!! I need this cheesecake in my life!","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Holly"},"datePublished":"2018-08-31"},{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"reviewBody":"You had me at Nutella!!","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Sarah"},"datePublished":"2018-08-31"}],"recipeCategory":["Dessert"],"recipeCuisine":["American"],"keywords":"easy no bake dessert, no bake cheesecake recipe, no bake nutella cheesecake, nutella cheesecake, nutella cheesecake recipe, nutella recipe, oreo recipe","nutrition":{"@type":"NutritionInformation","servingSize":"1 serving (1/8 recipe)","calories":"660 kcal","carbohydrateContent":"62 g","proteinContent":"7 g","fatContent":"44 g","saturatedFatContent":"26 g","cholesterolContent":"89 mg","sodiumContent":"391 mg","fiberContent":"2 g","sugarContent":"48 g","transFatContent":"0.3 g","unsaturatedFatContent":"15 g"},"@id":"https://fantabulosity.com/nutella-cheesecake-no-bake-filling-baked-brownie-crust/#recipe","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://fantabulosity.com/nutella-cheesecake-no-bake-filling-baked-brownie-crust/#article"},"mainEntityOfPage":"https://fantabulosity.com/nutella-cheesecake-no-bake-filling-baked-brownie-crust/"}]}</script>
