	<li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="comment-137323">
	<article id="article-comment-137323">

		
		<header class="comment-header">
			<p class="comment-author">
				<span class="comment-author-name">Cheryl</span> <span class="says">says</span>			</p>

			<p class="comment-meta"><time class="comment-time">February 07, 2026 at 1:30 pm</time></p>		</header>

		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>After making, recipe says put in freezer. Directions also state refrigerator in step by step on blog. Which is it?</p>
		</div>

		<div class="comment-reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-137323" data-commentid="137323" data-postid="23536" data-belowelement="article-comment-137323" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Cheryl" aria-label="Reply to Cheryl">Reply</a></div>
		
	</article>
	<ul class="children">

	<li class="comment byuser comment-author-jessica-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2--2 bypostauthor odd alt depth-2" id="comment-137335">
	<article id="article-comment-137335">

		
		<header class="comment-header">
			<p class="comment-author">
				<span class="comment-author-name">Jessica</span> <span class="says">says</span>			</p>

			<p class="comment-meta"><time class="comment-time">February 08, 2026 at 7:44 am</time></p>		</header>

		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>Hi Cheryl! Sorry for any confusion! Putting it in the freezer to &#8220;set&#8221; is recommended. If storing leftovers, it should be good for 4-5 days in the refrigerator, or up to 3 months in the freezer. I hope that helps!</p>
		</div>

		<div class="comment-reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-137335" data-commentid="137335" data-postid="23536" data-belowelement="article-comment-137335" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Jessica" aria-label="Reply to Jessica">Reply</a></div>
		
	</article>
	</li><!-- #comment-## -->
</ul><!-- .children -->
</li><!-- #comment-## -->

	<li class="comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="comment-57936">
